  "mindfulnessEntrySubtitle": "Mindfulness sessions are saved directly to Health Connect.",
  "mindfulnessEntryPermissionNeeded": "For the summary, OpenVitals only asks for view permissions. To add mindfulness entries, we need write permission. OpenVitals will not store these sessions; entries are saved in Health Connect.",
  "activityRecordingWithoutGpsTitle": "Record without GPS",
  "@activityRecordingWithoutGpsTitle": {
    "description": "Switch: record a running/cycling activity with no route, no location permission and no waiting for a fix."
