    "description": "Plainly states what a GPS-less recording loses. Everything listed is derived from location; things that are not (elevation, steps, heart rate) are still recorded."
  },
  "activityRecordingWithoutGpsWarningKept": "Duration, heart rate and elevation gain are still recorded, and you can type the distance in yourself when you save.",
  "@activityRecordingWithoutGpsWarningKept": {
    "description": "What a GPS-less recording DOES still capture. Elevation comes from the barometer, which needs no position."
  },
  "activityRecordingWithoutGpsWarningKeptSteps": "Duration, heart rate, elevation gain and your step count are still recorded, and you can type the distance in yourself when you save.",
  "@activityRecordingWithoutGpsWarningKeptSteps": {
